Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:16.06,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.26,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,凭由希奈目前的成绩而言是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.84,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,所谓不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.50,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,那是在尝尽所有可能性之后才能说出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:26.46,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,你已经尝试过所有的可能性了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:31.46,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,以现状 偏差值至少得提高30
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:33.12,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,举个不太恰当的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.42,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,必须得在接下来的18个月里要赶超50万人的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.26,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,你觉得这可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.56,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,她本人都说想要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.20,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,难不成你打算把她的梦想扼杀在摇篮之中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.66,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,别说摇篮了 都还没出生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.96,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,完全是在腹中就开始异想天开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:50.18,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,有志者事竟成 这种时候鼓励孩子去拼搏不该是教师的职责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:56.88,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,教师的职责是告诉孩子现实后在尽可能的范围内给与建议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:00.18,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,明明逆境才促使孩子成长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:03.10,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,这不是逆境 是有勇无谋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:08.06,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,本人的才能和努力都不够的结果就是现在的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.68,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,请您不要把您女儿跟您相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:14.24,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,人是各有不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.82,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,我期待老师您今后的教育成果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.58,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.16,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,对不起 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:31.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,白羽啊 我说啊 火星这东西根本就不能算志愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:36.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,您说的对…是目的地才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:37.96,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,问题不在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.66,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,再说移民火星的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.68,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,事到如今也没有实现的可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.85,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,这是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.02,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,早呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.98,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,美夏 我妈妈往哪边走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.24,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,哎 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:58.12,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,刚上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我妈妈手机忘拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:04.32,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,哦哦好酷联合国专用机 帅爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.86,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,妈妈你的手机 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:14.22,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,由希奈 火星人什么的是不存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.06,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:28.52,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,啊 好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.68,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,由希奈的妈妈好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:34.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,就是个不称职的妈妈罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.92,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,我家妈妈就只是个大婶而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:41.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,和她比起来啊 毕竟由希奈妈妈是研究所所长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.16,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,于是 志愿谈的怎么样了 填了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,火星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.22,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,哈？ 热的那边来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,冷的那边 不过我也是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.16,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我妈妈都不反对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.05,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,人生可要再认真点考虑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.46,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,但是为啥要填火星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.18,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我想去看看火星的运河啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.70,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,哎 真有那东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:09.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.82,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,应该是没有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.58,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,骗人 绝对蕴藏着河川的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.66,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,你啊 就是喜欢这些玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.32,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,火星的河阶也想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.82,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,听不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.34,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,话说那个不是你妈妈的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.87,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,啊 我给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.42,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,竟然能把这么重要的东西都落下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.24,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,真不愧是由希奈的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.12,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,不过 你也只能送过去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.84,Default,Takekuma,0,0,0,,哎 讨厌啦 我不想去那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:42.48,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,不要找借口了 跟我来吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.86,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,Let‘s go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.28,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,走了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.54,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,你好 索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.36,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,索菲也来做三方面谈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.14,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.30,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,不呢 我并没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.08,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,这样啊 索菲还小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.90,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我早就决定好了 只需要继续钻研目前的工作就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.26,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,由希奈同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.58,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.98,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,她要去火星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.94,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,火星？Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.92,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,对 就是火星人住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:23.78,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,玩笑还是适可而止的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:25.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.30,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,索菲现在去工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.66,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,嗯 那么贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.64,Default,both,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.28,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,那孩子真是厉害呢 毕竟是跳级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.80,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,而且据说还在联合国的研究所里任职
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.74,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,跟我们完全不是一类人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.38,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,啊 对了 请她帮我把手机捎过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.24,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,索菲帮我把这个带过去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.84,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,小姐 您的朋友追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.48,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,不要管 继续开就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:58.42,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:10.16,Default,both,0,0,0,,我要上车 我要上车 我要上车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.54,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,水位涨了 河道看起来都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.46,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,天天都在看你看不腻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.04,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,看不腻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.86,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.13,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,大坝啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.65,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还是一如既往的壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.86,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.28,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,回来的路上你想怎么看都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:21.82,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,好大啊 那些是由希奈妈妈造出来的来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.98,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,为什么你不愿意来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我不怎么喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.38,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,就像刚才的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.38,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,也对 你是所长的女儿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.53,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,周围的视线实在是总让人有种莫名其妙的紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,对 美夏的志愿里填了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.62,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,就职吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:00.66,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,去哪工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.10,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:06.60,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,像我种又没才能没耐性又没智商的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.88,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,哪肯要我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.76,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,就目前的成绩来看 有难度喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:15.46,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,亲戚们都说我是大器晚成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:19.06,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,所以如果用我的话 肯定能大显身手的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:23.28,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 看着美夏我觉得我也要努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:27.28,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,嗯 我怎么觉得好像被嘲讽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,错觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:32.10,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,那 我去给我爸爸个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,食堂那边来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.78,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,对对 我爸是厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.98,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,这个时候应该很闲 4点再见？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.14,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,好  待会见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.50,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:52.80,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,真是的 为什么不在学校给我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:57.38,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,总是这样子 完全不顾周围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:08:59.36,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:00.98,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:05.16,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,总之 要想去火星的话 不加把劲可不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.84,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我可不觉得那是加把劲就能解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.64,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,没问题 毕竟你可是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:12.86,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,别这么夸我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:17.87,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,啊对了 真要去的话 也得等小春长大点再去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,妈妈你也偶尔自己带带孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.04,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,哎呀 不是带大了由希奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我是伯父带大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:29.76,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,真是儿女不知父母心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.22,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,稍微加把劲 让班主任对你刮目相看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.32,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,也只有心情好的时候才摆出一副家长的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,接下来做点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.88,Default,Colonel,0,0,0,,确定不是弹道导弹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它的体积并不属于导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,轨道倾斜角98度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相对速度 秒速两公里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.16,Default,Colonel,0,0,0,,两公里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.26,Default,Colonel,0,0,0,,就陨石来说也太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Object1 捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,坠落地点预测完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,从Object1中出现了多个反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.22,Default,Colonel,0,0,0,,分裂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Object1正在减速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.28,Default,Colonel,0,0,0,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.60,Default,Takehito,0,0,0,,恶鬼还会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:42.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:50.00,Default,Takehito,0,0,0,,对 他们是从比遥远更遥远的世界回来吃人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.48,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:56.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,什么嘛 才这时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.27,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,荒俣先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.42,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,嗯？ 啊  由希酱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:12.46,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.52,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,来找洋海的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.52,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,我也跟她说过让她偶尔也回家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:21.74,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.24,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,洋海的女儿由希奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.18,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,原来如此 就是那孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:30.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那个东西 好像在哪见过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.08,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,它是“魔盒”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs51\pos(976,990)}the cube
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.74,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,60年前在隧道施工之中 从岩石破碎带之中发现的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:39.96,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,你知道得很详细嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.48,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不过这东西能随便给外人看么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.06,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:47.22,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,反正是早就世人皆知的上古遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,990)}Artifact
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.58,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,反正至今都没搞明白这东西是个什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:53.32,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,比起这东西下面那个巨人就好办多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:54.68,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,巨人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:59.12,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,那是尚未公开的另一个上古遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,990)}Artifact
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.34,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,同时也是在这里建立研究所的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,是什么理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.54,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,它动不了 也运不走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:12.10,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,但是那个与其说是巨人不如说是鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,鬼…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.22,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,白羽岳人教授
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:21.36,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,说来你的父亲有在调查这一带的传说吧
