Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.54,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,重力平衡器安定启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.08,Default,Liu Shen Mi,0,0,0,,稳定装置初始化
