Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:53.42,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,鬼的走狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.26,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,你想对由希奈干什么
